data.value: In Los Angeles, the heart of the American film industry, you can visit Hollywood and have a great time in entertainment parks like Disneyland and Universal Studios. Beverly Hills, on the other hand, attracts those who want to witness Hollywood's luxurious and magnificent life. Enjoy the ocean in Malibu and the famous Venice Beach, the choice of World stars, and spend time in cafes, bars and restaurants; and enjoy a pleasant stroll along the beach in Long Beach. Santa Calina can sail from island's white sand beaches; enjoy seafood with stunning sunset views.
